OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FTui Airways has been ranked among the
OL,7,Fworst airlines for UK flight
OL,8,Fpunctuality, with an average delay of
OL,9,F46 minutes for one of its routes.
OL,11,FThe airline's departures from UK
OL,12,Fairports were an average of 20 minutes
OL,13,Fand 24 seconds behind schedule in
OL,14,F2025, according to analysis of Civil
OL,15,FAviation Authority (CAA) data by the
OL,16,FPress Association.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
