FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FThe least punctual of its routes with
OL,7,Fat least 100 flights was from
OL,8,FBirmingham to the Greek island of
OL,9,FZante, which had an average delay of
OL,10,F46 minutes.
OL,12,FRory Boland, editor of consumer
OL,13,Fmagazine Which? Travel, said it was
OL,14,F"unacceptable" that airline passengers
OL,15,F"continue to face unreliable service"
OL,16,Famid fare rises.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@NO]wD@AOUwD@eO]
