OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FHe went on: "Airlines must do more to
OL,7,Fsupport travellers during delays,
OL,8,Fincluding clearly communicating their
OL,9,Frights and eligibility for
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,F"It's worth putting in a claim with
OL,13,Fyour airline if you think it's
OL,14,Fresponsible ` and escalating the
OL,15,Fcomplaint if it refuses to pay."
OL,26,@nD@MOUtD@AOUwD@`O]
