OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FTui Airways is owned by Tui Group,
OL,7,Fwhich also operates the UK's second
OL,8,Flargest package holiday company. Many
OL,9,Fof its holiday customers use the
OL,10,Fairline, which serves more than 20 UK
OL,11,Fairports.
OL,13,FThe punctuality analysis took into
OL,14,Faccount all scheduled and chartered
OL,15,Fdepartures from UK airports by the 34
OL,16,Fairlines which operated more than
OL,17,F2,500 of these flights last year.
OL,18,FCancelled flights were not included.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
