CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FAage Dunhaupt, Tui Group's director of
OL,7,Fcommunications, said: "We fully
OL,8,Funderstand that for holidaymakers,
OL,9,Fevery minute counts.
OL,11,F"Minimising delays remains a top
OL,12,Fpriority, and our teams work
OL,13,Fcontinuously to improve operational
OL,14,Fperformance across our network."
OL,26,@oD@WOUsD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
