CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FMr Dunhaupt said the airline makes "a
OL,7,Fconscious choice" to operate flights
OL,8,F"wherever possible, even if they are
OL,9,Fdelayed, rather than cancelling them",
OL,10,Fas this ensures passengers reach their
OL,11,Fdestination "rather than facing the
OL,12,Frisk of extended disruption".
OL,14,FHe added: "If we were to follow
OL,15,Fbroader industry practices of
OL,16,Fcancelling flights more readily, our
OL,17,Fpunctuality ranking would improve
OL,18,Fsignificantly. However, this would
OL,19,Fcome at the expense of our customers."
OL,26,@nD@dOUoD@QO]pD@AOUqD@eO]sD@MOUtD@\O]vD@
OL,26,AKOU{D@fO]
