OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FTui Airways was ranked the fifth worst
OL,7,Fairline for punctuality, according to
OL,8,Fthe new analysis.
OL,10,FAir India had the poorest record for
OL,11,Fthe second year in a row, with an
OL,12,Faverage delay of 36 minutes and 36
OL,13,Fseconds.
OL,15,FIt was followed by Blue Islands (25
OL,16,Fminutes and 12 seconds) ` a regional
OL,17,Fairline based in the Channel Islands
OL,18,Fwhich collapsed in November 2025 ` TAP
OL,19,FAir Portugal (23 minutes) and Saudia
OL,20,F(21 minutes and 18 seconds).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
