OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FScandinavian Airlines recorded the
OL,7,Fbest performance last year, with UK
OL,8,Fdepartures delayed by an average of
OL,9,Feight minutes, ahead of Virgin
OL,10,FAtlantic (11 minutes).
OL,12,FThe average delay for airlines
OL,13,Fincluded in the analysis was 14
OL,14,Fminutes and 48 seconds, down from 18
OL,15,Fminutes and 18 seconds in 2024.
OL,17,FWhat could passengers be entitled to
OL,18,Ffollowing significant delays?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
