PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FCAA director Tim Johnson said the
OL,7,Fauthority recognises the "impact" and
OL,8,F"inconvenience" significant disruption
OL,9,Fcan have on passengers, which is why
OL,10,Fthere "are rules in place to protect
OL,11,Fpassengers".
OL,13,F"Airlines are expected to minimise the
OL,14,Fimpact of delays where possible, by
OL,15,Fproviding timely information and
OL,16,Fupholding passengers' rights during
OL,17,Fdisruption," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
