PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FDepending on the distance of the route
OL,7,Fand length of delay, passengers booked
OL,8,Fon flights from the UK that are
OL,9,Frunning behind schedule are entitled
OL,10,Fto assistance such as a reasonable
OL,11,Famount of food and drink, a means to
OL,12,Fcommunicate and overnight
OL,13,Faccommodation if required.
OL,15,FPassengers may also be able to claim
OL,16,Fcompensation of up to #520 from the
OL,17,Fairline if the reason for the delay is
OL,18,Fdeemed within its control, which could
OL,19,Fbe a fault with the aircraft or pilot
OL,20,Fsickness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
