FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782152300
OL,3,CTui among worst airlines for UK flight
OL,4,Cdelays, new analysis shows
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Airlines UK, a
OL,7,Ftrade body for UK-registered carriers,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The vast majority of UK airline
OL,9,Fflights depart on time and CAA data
OL,10,Fshows customer satisfaction levels are
OL,11,Fat an all-time high.
OL,13,F"Most delays are the result of issues
OL,14,Fthat are entirely outside airline
OL,15,Fcontrol, such as adverse weather,
OL,16,Fforced reductions in the number of
OL,17,Fplanes that are able to land and take
OL,18,Foff each hour, and industrial action.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
